#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "User Guide"
msgstr "Korisnički vodič"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Welcome to &kamoso;!"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<application>Kamoso</application> is a great program to use your webcam "
#| "to take pictures or make videos. It probably should be the best webcam "
#| "recorder for &Linux;. This guide will help you use Kamoso once you have "
#| "installed it. We tried to make it simple and friendly. Good luck!"
msgid ""
"&kamoso; is a great program to use your webcam to take pictures or make "
"videos. This guide will help you to use &kamoso; once you have installed it."
msgstr ""
"<application>Kamoso</application>je odličan program da koristite vašu web "
"kameru za pravljenje slika ili videa. Vjerovatno bi trebao biti najbolji za "
"snimanje web amerom za &Linux; Ovaj vodič će vam pomoći u korištenju Kamoso "
"kada ga instalirate. Pokušali smo napraviti ga jednostavnim i prijateljskim. "
"Sretno!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "Brzi početak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On launching &kamoso;, it displays this window with buttons at the bottom:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to <guibutton>Shoot</guibutton> mode to take one picture"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch to <guibutton>Burst</guibutton> mode and take continuously pictures "
"until you stop by clicking the middle button again"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to <guibutton>Record</guibutton> mode to record a video"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start or stop taking pictures or recording a video"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show gallery"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show settings"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pictures and videos are numbered consecutively and saved automatically in "
"the <guilabel>Captures directory</guilabel> defined in the settings."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing Captures"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view and manage your captured pictures or videos click the "
"<guibutton>Show gallery</guibutton> button. In the context menu for each "
"entry in the gallery you find actions to manage them:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guimenuitem>Open</guimenuitem> to view your captures in the associated "
"application."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to delete pictures and videos open the captures folder in the "
"filemanager."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next actions allow you to upload captures to the Internet or send them "
"to a contact or device."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guimenuitem>Save as</guimenuitem> to copy the complete content of the "
"gallery to a new folder."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:128
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Customising"
msgid "Customizing"
msgstr "Prilagođavanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Show settings</guibutton> button to open the settings "
"panel. Click the button again to hide the settings panel."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you want to change the directory where <application>Kamoso</"
#| "application> saves the pictures, navigate to the <guilabel>General</"
#| "guilabel> panel, and change the directory from thereon."
msgid ""
"If you want to change the folder where &kamoso; saves pictures and videos, "
"change the <guilabel>Captures directory</guilabel> at the top."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da promijenite direktorij gdje <application>Kamoso</application> "
"sprema slike, idite na  <guilabel>Generalno</guilabel> panel, i promijenite "
"direktorij odatle."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable <guibutton>Use flash</guibutton> to highlight the window before "
"taking photos."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the sliders you can modify camera settings like brightness, hue, "
"contrast, saturation and gamma."
msgstr ""

