#~ msgid "2012-12-05"
#~ msgstr "2012-12-05"

#~ msgid "2.0.2 (&kde; SC 4.10)"
#~ msgstr "2.0.2 (&kde; SC 4.10)"

#~ msgid "Welcome to <application>Kamoso</application>!"
#~ msgstr "Dobrodošli u <application>Kamoso</application>!"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "On launching <application>Kamoso</application>, you are greeted with two "
#~ "groups of buttons on the left and right, and a button in the center."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Pri pokretanju <application>Kamoso</application>, pozdravljeni ste sa "
#~ "dvije grupe dugmadi desno i lijevo, i drugmetom u centru."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The central button helps you to click a picture! Go ahead and try it now! "
#~ "SMILE!"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ovo centralno dugme vam pomaže da napravite sliku! Idite i pokšajte to "
#~ "sada! OSMIJEH!"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<application>Kamoso</application> will give you a 3 second heads up so "
#~ "you can pose for your picture, and ask you to smile right before clicking!"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<application>Kamoso</application> vam daje 3 sekunde prednosti da možete "
#~ "pozirati za sliku, i traži vam da se nasmijete tačno prije klikanja."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you click on the second button from the left, <application>Kamoso</"
#~ "application> changes to burst-mode. <application>Kamoso</application> "
#~ "will keep clicking pictures rapidly till you don't click on the center "
#~ "button and tell it to stop. The pictures line up in chronological order "
#~ "on the bottom, and you can view them by double-clicking them. "
#~ "Alternatively, you could right click and choose <guilabel>Open</guilabel> "
#~ "to view the pictures too! If you aren't happy with any of the pictures, "
#~ "just right click and select <guilabel>Trash</guilabel> to delete that "
#~ "particular picture."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ako kliknete na drugo dugme lijevo, <application>Kamoso</application> "
#~ "mijenja mod u prasak-mod. <application>Kamoso</application> će slikati "
#~ "brzo dok ne klliknete na centralno dugme i kažete mu da prestane. Linija "
#~ "slika u hronološkom redu je na dnu i možete ih vidjet duplim-klikom na "
#~ "njih. Altrenativno možete kliknuti denim klikom i odabrati "
#~ "<guilabel>Otvori</guilabel>   da vidite slike takođe! Ako niste "
#~ "zadovoljni ni sa jednom slikom, kliknite desni klik i odaberite "
#~ "<guilabel>Smeće</guilabel> da obrišete tu sliku."

#~ msgid "Upload image to Facebook"
#~ msgstr "Postavite sliku na Facebook"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you feel your newly-clicked pictures must be uploaded to your Facebook "
#~ "profile, just right click on the picture and select <guilabel>Facebook "
#~ "Import/Export</guilabel>. A window will open up on your browser asking "
#~ "you to grant permission to <application>Kamoso</application>. Once you do "
#~ "this, upload away!"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ako mislite da vaše novo-uslikane slike moraju biti postavljene na vaš "
#~ "Facebook profil, samo kliknite desni klik na sliku i odaberite "
#~ "<guilabel>Facebook Import/Export</guilabel>. Otvorit će se prozor vašeg "
#~ "pretraživaca koji vam traži odobrenje dozvole za  <application>Kamoso</"
#~ "application>. Kada ovo uradite, samo postavite sliku!"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You need to have an account on Facebook to upload the picture you made"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Morate da imate profil na Facebooku da postavite slike koje ste napravili."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you want to avoid all the right clicks, click on the second button on "
#~ "the right side and you'll be provided with the same options as when you "
#~ "right click."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ako želite da izbjegnete svo desno klikanje, kliknite na drugo dugme na "
#~ "desnoj strani i obezbjedit će vam se iste opcija kao i kada biste desno "
#~ "klikali."

#~ msgid "Upload video to YouTube"
#~ msgstr "Postavite video na YouTube."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<application>Kamoso</application> also allows you to capture videos! By "
#~ "clicking on the red button on the left, you change to video mode. Click "
#~ "on the central button to shoot your video! Right click on the video and "
#~ "select <guilabel>YouTube</guilabel> to upload it to YouTube."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<application>Kamoso</application> vam takođe omogućuje da snimite videe! "
#~ "Klikom na crveno dugmo lijevo, mijenjate u video mod. Kliknite na "
#~ "centralno dugme da snimite video. Kliknite desnim klikom na video i "
#~ "odaberite  <guilabel>YouTube</guilabel> da ga postavite na YouTube."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You need to have an account on YouTube and provide <application>Kamoso</"
#~ "application> an access with your username and password – don't worry, "
#~ "it's totally safe!"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Morate da imate račun na YouTubeu i omogućite <application>Kamoso</"
#~ "application> pristup sa vašim koriničkim imenom i šifrom - ne brinite, "
#~ "potpuno je sigurno!"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you feel your picture quality isn't optimal, click on the button on "
#~ "the extreme right and select <guilabel>Settings</guilabel>. This is the "
#~ "settings panel."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ako mislite da kvaliteta vaše slike nije optimalna, kliknite na "
#~ "najljevlje dugme i odaberite <guilabel>Postavke</guilabel>. Ovo je panel "
#~ "postavki."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you want to change the time before <application>Kamoso</application> "
#~ "clicks your picture, navigate to <guilabel>Photo settings</guilabel>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ako želite da pormijenite vrijeme prije nego <application>Kamoso</"
#~ "application> napravi sliku, otiđite na <guilabel>Postavke slike</"
#~ "guilabel>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you're a really technical user, scroll over to the <guilabel>Video "
#~ "settings</guilabel> and there you can adjust settings like brightness, "
#~ "contrast, &etc;"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ako ste zaista tehnički korisnik, skrolujte do  <guilabel>Video postavke</"
#~ "guilabel> i tamo prilagodite postavke kao svjetlost, kontrast, &etc;"

#~ msgid "The End"
#~ msgstr "Kraj"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Well, we've reached the end of our tutorial. I hope your queries have "
#~ "been adequately answered!"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Dakle, došli smo do kraja ovog tutorijala. Nadamo se da su vaša pitanje "
#~ "adekvatno odgovorena."

#~ msgid "Enjoy using <application>Kamoso</application>!"
#~ msgstr "Uživajte kroisteći <application>Kamoso</application>!"
